overview: "The user initiated a request to significantly improve the aesthetics
  of their sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was too generic. The
  agent conducted a thorough review of the existing styling, identifying a need
  for a more calming, sleep-themed design. The approach involved a multi-faceted
  update: introducing a new OKLCH-based color palette, redesigning the main form
  layout with subtle background elements and an improved progress indicator, and
  enhancing the styling of all UI components like checkboxes, radio buttons,
  sliders, and cards. Crucially, all questionnaire sections were updated to use
  consistent, themed grouping boxes and typography. The report section's card
  headers and content colors were also harmonized with the new theme.
